---
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets';
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import mePhoto from '../assets/me.jpg';
import umdPhoto from '../assets/umd.jpg';
import ideaFactoryPhoto from '../assets/ideafactory.jpg';
import signature from '../assets/signature.png';

const likes = [
  "Family", "Friends", "Effective Altruism", "Longevity",
  "Philosophy", "Side Projects", "Technology", "Minimalism",
  "Maximalism", "Entrepreneurship", "Sushi", "Meditation",
  "Light Blue", "LLMs", "Space", "Surrealism", "Stoicism", "San Francisco",
  "Cozy Cabins", "Studio Ghibli", "Stickman Fight Animations", "Open-Mindedness",
];

const dislikes = [
  "Coffee", "Social Media", "Notifications", "Narrow-mindedness", "Alcohol",
  "Pessimism", "Arguments", "Berries", "Ads", "Reality TV",
  "Group chats", "Politics", "Drama", "Wasps", "All-nighters",
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About · Andrew Ghosh"
  description="A bit about Andrew Ghosh."
>
  <h1 class="page-title">Andrew Mark Ghosh</h1>
  <p class="page-tagline">That's my full name. I'm 19. Here's more stuff about me:</p>

  <figure class="about__figure">
    <Picture
      class="about__photo"
      src={mePhoto}
      formats={['avif', 'webp']}
      alt="Andrew Ghosh"
      width={360}
      densities={[1, 2]}
    />
    <figcaption class="about__caption">
      Selfie I took from my Mac while making this site.
    </figcaption>
  </figure>

  <p>
    The summer before I started college I was trying to figure out what I wanted to do with my life.
    After lots of pondering, I came to some conclusions.
  </p>
    

 <p>
 My ideal life goes like this:
 </p>

 <ol>
    <li>Launch a successful tech startup</li>
    <li>Feel good about myself because it had actual value and made millions of people's lives better</li>
    <li>Use my wealth to fund human longevity research</li>
    <li>Either start my own longevity thing or just dive into my interests</li>
  </ol>
  <p>
    Since that summer, I've tried and failed at 3 startups. I'm currently on my 4th, NutrifyUMD (meal planning app for UMD students).
  </p>
  <h2 class="taste__heading">Likes <span class="taste__emoji">😄</span></h2>
  <ul class="taste taste--like">
    {likes.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
  </ul>

  <h2 class="taste__heading">Dislikes <span class="taste__emoji">😒</span></h2>
  <ul class="taste taste--dislike">
    {dislikes.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
  </ul>

  <p>
    Fun facts:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Lived in New York, New Jersey, Texas, and Maryland.</li>
    <li>Traveled to Japan, Armenia, Hong Kong, and Jamaica.</li>
    <li>Can solve 3x3, 2x2, and pyraminx rubik's puzzles.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    Accomplishments:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>1st place in marathon (19 & Under, 2024 International Peace Marathon)</li>
    <li>Top 1% test score (2023 PSAT National Merit Commended Student)</li>
    <li>Marathon was 26 miles/42 kilometers | 3.7 million people took the PSAT</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    Also I don't like full minimalism, I like minimalism with cool sparks here and there. 
    That's one reason I love campus; most buildings have the staple mostly brick + white highlights look with similar (beautifully simple) architetcure, 
  </p>

  <figure class="about__figure">
    <Picture
      class="about__photo"
      src={umdPhoto}
      formats={['avif', 'webp']}
      alt="A classic brick-and-white University of Maryland building"
      width={360}
      densities={[1, 2]}
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </figure>
    
  <p>
    and then randomly you'll see a crazy cool colorful looking building.
    I'm lucky enough to be in my favorite one every day: the IDEA factory.
  </p>

  <figure class="about__figure">
    <Picture
      class="about__photo"
      src={ideaFactoryPhoto}
      formats={['avif', 'webp']}
      alt="The colorful IDEA Factory building at the University of Maryland"
      width={360}
      densities={[1, 2]}
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <figcaption class="about__caption">
      You can see the Startup Shell space in the bottom left.
    </figcaption>
  </figure>
  <p>
    I don't use social media and am on LinkedIn once a month so the best way to contact me is just via cal or email.
  </p>
  <p>
    Email: <a href="mailto:thisisandrewmg@gmail.com">thisisandrewmg@gmail.com</a>
  </p>
  <p>
    LinkedIn: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/andrew-ghosh-788684354/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">linkedin.com/in/andrew-ghosh</a>
  </p>
  <p>
    Chat: <a href="https://cal.com/andrew-ghosh-o6rtxi/quick-chat" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">cal.com/andrew-ghosh-o6rtxi/quick-chat</a>
  </p>

  <figure class="about__figure about__figure--signature">
    <Picture
      class="about__signature"
      src={signature}
      formats={['webp']}
      alt="Andrew Ghosh's signature"
      width={280}
      densities={[1, 2]}
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </figure>
  
</BaseLayout>
